channel.title: Choob Isle Final Development
channel.description:
Hello, welcome to the Choob Isle Final Development thread. Choob Isle v1 has seen enough days and v2 was never completed. I would like to start a development team to create a new server called "Choob Isle Final." Which will be the last in the series. What I will do is put together a Coding Team and a Testing Team. If you would like to join please leave an application here in this format.
[code][b]Position:[/b] [i]Put the position you want to join here. (Coder/Tester)[/i] [b]Reliability:[/b] [i]Indicate whether or not you will be a reliable person.[/i] [b]Time Zone:[/b] [i]I need to know your time zone so I can call for people at good times[/i] [b]Experience w/ Selected Position:[/b] [i]Indicate your personal experience with your selected position[/i] [b]Experience Proof:[/b] [i]Please give some evidence that you have done something of the sort before[/i] [b]Contact Option:[/b] [i]Please give me some form of contact that I can reach you at[/i][/code]
[b]*Note*[/b] - [i]Please keep in mind, I will pick the best that fit the position. Even if someone posts to help before another, I may choose someone over that person.[/i]
[b]*Note*[/b] - [i]This is a note to all MoparScape Members wanting to help out with the development process. Please check out our [url=http://www.codersrus.org]website[/url] and register at our [url=http://www.codersrus.org/smf]forums[/url].[/i]
Here are the positions and their current members: -----------------------------------------------
[b]Coders:[/b] [b]-------[/b] 1. Coder Quack - jonthemod55@hotmail.com 2. 3. 4. 5.
[b]Testers:[/b] [b]--------[/b] 1. Cursed 2. Samyyy123 3. Jax 4. 5. 6. 7. 8. 9. 10.
Remember MoparScape Members, if you plan on signing up, please register at our [url=http://www.codersrus.org/smf]forums[/url].
[b]Goals:[/b] ----- Add Every skill (full) Add anti-cheat packages Keep it lag free [s]Website[/s] Never before seen Mini-Games 24/7 Hosting Dedicated Server Client Full Jad Mini-Game Full Castle Wars Full Fight Pits Much Much More...
[b]Complete:[/b] --------- Website (www.codersrus.org) Full Mining Full Woodcutting Full Fletching (With Interfaces)
Thank you, Mod Adam
